# ===== PULL MOBILE APP - PRODUCTION (Aurora Hall demo) =====
# We point at Cloudflare Pages because its Function proxies /api/v1/* to
# the Fly.io API. The proxy avoids DNS issues on networks that block fly.dev
# and removes any CORS handling for the mobile client (same origin from the
# pages.dev host).
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://aurora-hall.pages.dev/api/v1
